data.description: Escape to the country on this 7.59 acre equestrian property. Towering trees line the driveway, providing cool shade as you approach the charming 3 bed, 2 bath home. Just beyond the back patio lies a sprawling 120 x 200 foot riding arena - plenty of space to ride and rope to your heart's content. Inside, an open concept living and dining area create a light filled communal space. Large picture window in the living room provide an airy feel, complemented by a cozy gas fireplace for chilly country nights. Just off the dining area, the updated kitchen features stainless steel appliances and ample cabinetry storage. Down the hall, the 2 well-sized bedrooms provide private spaces to recharge. The master suite boasts a large closet area and en-suite bath. Outdoors, a spacious backyard beckons for relaxation under mature trees. Nearby, find sturdy horse pens with shelters where your equine companions can happily reside. Beyond, the huge partially fenced pasture spans over 4 acres, allowing horses to roam and graze freely on the lush acreage. Don't miss this rare opportunity to own a fantastic equestrian property. Schedule your showing today and start planning your idyllic country home.
